Summary: Describes the 'operator' property and its setter/getter methods for specifying the transform operation type.

Property: Operator (enum VisualShaderNodeTransformOp_Operator): The type of operation to be performed on the transforms. Default: 0.  
Method: set_operator(value: enum VisualShaderNodeTransformOp_Operator) → void  
Method: get_operator() → enum VisualShaderNodeTransformOp_Operator  
Note: This determines how transforms are combined or modified in the shader.